      "text": "心配性だねー。いざとなったらkana一人でも\nライブはきっちりこなしてみせるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're a worrier‚ aren't you? If push comes to shove‚\nI'm sure Kana will be able to handle\nthe live show just fine on me own.",
